title: Khokababu
subTitle: Abir Roy falls in love with his employer's younger sister. His employer, however, happens to be a dangerous gangster and is overprotective of his sister.

subTitle: A young man and a woman keep falling deeper in love every time they meet, regardless of the circumstances. However, they face many challenges in their path to unite with each other.

subTitle: Mainadevi requests Lord Shiva to choose between the curse and his love for Parvati. Tarakasura conspires against Mainadevi.

title: Dwiragaman
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Bakul Priya
subTitle: Before leaving for the city, Bakul promises Priya that they would get married once he returns. His father, however, plays tyrant and convinces Priya's father to get her married to someone else.

subTitle: A man who aspires to become a gangster arrives in London to achieve his dreams. However, complications arise when he meets a woman and falls in love with her.

title: Annadata
subTitle: Sankar's life changes when he gets taken in by a rich businessman. Years later, an opportunity arises for him to prove his loyalty to his adopted family.

title: Indrajit
subTitle: Indrajit is an honest police officer who punishes Raja, an MLA's son, for raping a girl. The MLA then kidnaps the former's son and demands Raja's release.

title: Fighter, Marbo Noy Morbo
subTitle: Surya, a college student, decides to exact revenge on a local gangster after he frames and kills his elder brother, ACP Bose.

title: Ghawre Bairey Aaj
subTitle: A contemporary retelling of the love triangle involving Nikhilesh, Sandip and Bimala.

title: Ghawre Bairey Aaj

title: Raktomukhi Neela
subTitle: Byomkesh becomes curious when Ramanath, a jewel thief, is released from Alipur jail. Later, Maharaja Ramendra Singha seeks his help and asks him to investigate the murder of his associate Haripada Rakshit.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Parvati feels joyful when Lord Shiva gets disguised as a woman to meet her. Mainadevi tries to convince Parvati not to marry Lord Shiva.

title: Agni Yudha
subTitle: A brother and sister duo share a loving relationship. However, things take a turn when the sister falls in love with a young man.

title: Amazon Obhijaan
subTitle: Anna, an Italian woman, approaches Shankar, an explorer, to accompany her in search of the golden city of El Dorado and he accepts the offer and sets out on an adventure through the Amazon.

subTitle: Joy aspires to be a police inspector like his father, an honest police constable. As his father meets the local anti-social thug, the situation shifts and conflicts arise.

title: Sedin Dekha Hoyechilo
subTitle: Kavita's father holds his daughter's lover's friends captive and asks them to reveal the couple's whereabouts. However, one of the boys, Abir, falls in love with his other daughter, Nandini.

title: Nater Guru
subTitle: A terrible heart attack leaves Sulochana in a vulnerable position. To ease her burdens, Sulochana's daughter reaches out to her estranged husband for help.

title: Bindaas
subTitle: Abhi falls in love with Kajol and convinces her family to get them married. However, things get complicated when Kajol's uncle asks him to kill their rival's son, who is none other than Abhi himself.

title: Eagoler Chokh
subTitle: A senior police officer and his assistant investigate a young woman's murder. As the case unfolds, he learns more about human psychology and the intricacies of his own mind.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Tarakasura sends an assassin to kill Mainadevi and plans to frame Lord Shiva. The assassin puts poison in Mainadevi's food.

title: Premer Pratidan
subTitle: Besotted with Radha, Sandip journeys to Shimla to profess his love. Though he eventually wins her heart, their newfound happiness proves fleeting.

title: Mahapith Tarapith
subTitle: Sameer Roy, a lawyer, is a devotee of Tara Maa while his friend, Ajay, does not believe in God. When Ajay's son falls sick, Sameer believes that only Tara Maa can save him.

title: Mahaguru
subTitle: Rudra Sen, a brave officer and an encounter specialist, is killed in the line of duty by a gangster. However, things become complicated when his doppelganger decides to take his place and avenge him.

title: Sathi

title: Chore Chore Mastuto Bhai
subTitle: John is hired by Nagraj to steal a diamond but ends up betraying him, inviting his ire. Before Nagraj's henchman kills John, he gives the diamond to a taxi driver for safekeeping.

title: Challenge
subTitle: Pooja, the daughter of a ruthless businessman who cannot tolerate any male advances towards her, falls for Abir. However, when her father learns about their relationship, all hell breaks loose.

title: Badla
subTitle: Bharti Devi leads a happy life with her three sons, Jay, Sujay and Arjun. However, Sanatan decides to break their family apart in order to settle past scores with Bharti, who he believes wronged him.
